jobInfo.postDescription:
Educational Background
- Bachelor’s degree or higher in related / relevant technical discipline. Such as electronics information, communication engineering, automatic controlling, computer science.

Technical Skills
- At least 3 years of work experience as a software engineer.
- Key skills: ability to work autonomously in an international environment creativity, team spirit and a pro-active attitude are imperative
- Excellent communication skills
- Experience in software module and integration testing
- Experience in software engineering techniques
- Knowledge of micro-controller hardware and peripherals
- Knowledge of automotive networks (CAN, LIN, K-Line) is considered an advantage


Language Skills
-	Fluent English is a must.

IT Skills
-To be skilled at Microsoft office.

Soft Skills
-Good communication skills in a global international company.
-Good management of multi-task, multi-customer.
- Open mind and ready for new knowledge
- Technical interface between customer, supplier and IEE development centers
- Support the technical discussion with customers.
- Coordinate the IEE internal software development activities.
- Set up good communication channel between IEE China and other IEE offices.

brandComInfo.introduce:
IEE集团公司总部位于欧洲卢森堡，控股公司为央企航天科技控股集团股份有限公司。集团公司分布在欧洲，亚洲，美国和墨西哥。
中国区生产基地位于河北廊坊经济技术开发区，人员规模500人左右，包括生产车间、物流、行政人事财务等人员，北京技术服务分公司位于丰台区海鹰路6号院2号楼2层，人员规模40人左右，涵盖研发、销售及工程项目人员，公司主营产品为汽车电子传感器。
